**Transformation Graph** — not knowledge graph, not social graph.

Registry + Encyclopedia + Ownership support the graph. Content is a byproduct.

## Build Order

1. Encyclopedia Engine (PASS-007) ✅
2. Path Engine (PASS-008) ✅
